query:
UPDATE mod_versions mv
                SET name = $1,
                version = $2,
                download_link = $3,
                hash = $4,
                geode_major = $5,
                geode_minor = $6,
                geode_patch = $7,
                geode_meta = $8,
                early_load = $9,
                api = $10,
                description = $11,
                updated_at = NOW()
            FROM mod_version_statuses mvs
            WHERE mv.status_id = mvs.id
            AND mvs.status = 'pending'
            AND mv.id = $12
